  <div class="disclaimer">⚠️<span class="disclaimer-text">Pokémon list sourced from <a href="https://serebii.net/pokemonchampions/pokemon.shtml" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Serebii.net</a> — subject to change as the game updates.</span></div>

